Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.25,0:00:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 愛到出神陶醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.42,0:00:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳愛到懊惱萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.46,0:00:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.74,0:00:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳無法忘記妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.04,0:00:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風兒硬是拆開\N我們纏綿甜蜜的吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.02,0:00:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面對無法停止的熾熱心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.36,0:00:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.06,0:00:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人無法討厭的冷漠態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.30,0:00:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見不到面令我痛苦萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.17,0:01:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳鬱悶不樂的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.37,0:01:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令我心碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.28,0:01:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.42,0:01:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.56,0:01:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.38,0:01:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,小津江,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.85,0:01:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣急著走,是要去約會嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.19,0:01:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.63,0:01:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,累死了,肩膀好酸喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.50,0:02:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,章魚教授的課\N真是累死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.37,0:02:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去原宿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.40,0:02:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要去呢\N那種小孩子去的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.90,0:02:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們餓不餓?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.87,0:02:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.91,0:02:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要請客嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.18,0:02:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要大杯的聖代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.18,0:02:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋,自己的份自己付錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.86,0:02:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦!真的假的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.33,0:02:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.93,0:02:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了,這種事很普通吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.43,0:02:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理所當然的,對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.30,0:02:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.43,0:02:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒什麼好大驚小怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.94,0:02:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江,妳也有男朋友,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.94,0:02:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼來著?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.44,0:02:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.78,0:02:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人\N沒有一起去旅行過嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.15,0:02:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.65,0:02:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們交往很久了,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.85,0:02:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.05,0:02:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你們進展到什麼地步?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.05,0:02:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼地步…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.49,0:03:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,五代不是那種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.99,0:03:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.40,0:03:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.93,0:03:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說,小津江妳的情況是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.87,0:03:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牽牽小手啊,摟摟肩膀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.04,0:03:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們一直維持\N這樣的關係而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.41,0:03:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是,這都還沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.25,0:03:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是不是有問題啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼問題啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.25,0:03:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說,這太不正常了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.25,0:03:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對?\N是有點不正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.32,0:03:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.00,0:03:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#38 五代失戀?\N小津江突然接近三鷹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.47,0:04:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好喔,要跟小津江約會嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.87,0:04:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很受歡迎喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.41,0:05:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.22,0:05:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快點的話\N管理員就要回來了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.32,0:05:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就請你放開我的手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.59,0:05:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意請我吃一客\N上等的炸蝦飯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.06,0:05:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要上等的唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.47,0:05:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.10,0:05:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了上等的炸蝦飯喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.77,0:05:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰理你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.91,0:05:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.65,0:05:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.95,0:05:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.25,0:05:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,我們走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.49,0:05:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去約會嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.16,0:05:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦…\N你的領帶歪掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.06,0:05:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼約會啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會太緊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.96,0:05:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.64,0:06:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.37,0:06:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.08,0:06:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.72,0:06:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是鴿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.18,0:06:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,是老虎耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.31,0:06:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代你看,老虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.53,0:07:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那隻老虎都不動耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.24,0:07:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.47,0:07:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我在叫你啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.92,0:07:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?妳在叫我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.52,0:07:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.26,0:07:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒什麼精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我精神好得很啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.70,0:07:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的領帶很緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.30,0:07:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?領帶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.24,0:07:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去喝點什麼吧\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.52,0:07:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.02,0:07:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心會濺出來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.16,0:08:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看電影會不會比較好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.20,0:08:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,這裡好玩多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.87,0:08:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.27,0:08:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,快來看,快來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.04,0:08:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看,那裡有一條好大的鯉魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.61,0:08:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.51,0:08:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,那裡也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.08,0:08:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兩條是一對的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微散步一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.89,0:09:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多該回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.06,0:09:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.03,0:09:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要不要來我家?\N來我家吃個晚飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.33,0:09:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.84,0:09:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不了,今天不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.17,0:09:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.31,0:09:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為上次才剛去\N妳家吃過飯沒多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.18,0:09:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.93,0:09:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.86,0:09:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,我當妳的暖爐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.67,0:09:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好溫暖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.74,0:09:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江,妳怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.91,0:10:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,沒什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會冷嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.16,0:10:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,好冷好冷喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.50,0:10:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就快回家吧,不然會感冒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.39,0:10:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不找五代一起來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.56,0:10:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有叫他來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.73,0:10:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他為什麼不來呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.16,0:10:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.30,0:10:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊,妳被甩了,對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.34,0:11:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛喔,妳幹嘛打我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.24,0:11:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個感情好得很呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.38,0:11:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳已經下定決心了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.25,0:11:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼決心?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.72,0:11:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼,畢竟五代是個男人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.22,0:11:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯的時候請不要看報紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.55,0:12:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.57,0:12:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場出名的橋段來自
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.44,0:12:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法國劇作家艾德蒙羅斯丹名作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.38,0:12:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''大鼻子情聖西哈諾''\N的最後一場戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫生兼音樂家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.55,0:13:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文武雙全的西哈諾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.72,0:13:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻因為有一個大鼻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.36,0:13:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迫使他放棄了\N他畢生唯一一段的戀情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.43,0:13:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅珊妮愛上俊美男子克里斯廷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.37,0:13:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文采洋溢的西哈諾\N代替克里斯廷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.94,0:13:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從戰場寫情書給羅珊妮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.49,0:13:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對對,手肘再伸長一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.49,0:13:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎?\N基本動作是最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,再來一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.99,0:14:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,讓你破費請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.12,0:14:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣,妳就儘量吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以這樣,不好意思啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.23,0:14:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣,別客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.00,0:14:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.37,0:14:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我還要起司蛋糕和檸檬紅茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各一個是嗎?馬上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.57,0:14:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳總是這麼有精神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.94,0:14:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有呢\N其實我的心情很沮喪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.58,0:14:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.29,0:14:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男生都到底在想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.93,0:14:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟五代出了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.90,0:14:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題就在什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.43,0:14:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代是不是\N有其他喜歡的女生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.81,0:15:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,這女孩子還不知道\N五代喜歡音無小姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.62,0:15:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛就像賭博一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是以朋友的感覺相處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.66,0:15:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當說出''我喜歡妳''之後\N關係可能就會結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.07,0:15:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不說那句話的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.54,0:15:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還能一直交往下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.07,0:15:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.87,0:15:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代只是膽子小而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.14,0:15:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.38,0:15:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.12,0:15:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點冷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.79,0:15:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走,回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.44,0:16:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.37,0:16:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會\N希望還有機會能跟你聊天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.68,0:16:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題,隨時歡迎來找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.01,0:16:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?我好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.65,0:16:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.62,0:16:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.64,0:16:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!三鷹和小津江?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.78,0:16:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個組合真令人難以置信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.41,0:16:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.12,0:16:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託,這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.52,0:16:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我怎麼知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.32,0:16:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看是小津江移情別戀了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.26,0:16:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.63,0:17:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是個帥哥嗎?有錢嗎?\N有車嗎?個性開朗嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.67,0:17:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.87,0:17:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勝負已經揭曉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.54,0:17:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代贏的機會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.71,0:17:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.16,0:17:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代跟小津江的感情怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.23,0:17:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?你問我這個做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.87,0:17:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為上次我見到小津江…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個壞胚子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.02,0:17:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先把五代的女朋友搶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.59,0:18:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後還來探聽\N他們之間感情的龜裂狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.53,0:18:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.66,0:18:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要裝傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.93,0:18:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天有人看到\N你跟小津江抱在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.93,0:18:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.27,0:18:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.77,0:18:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟小津江才沒有做那種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.57,0:18:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.82,0:18:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近五代跟我見面\N也都不會對我笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.40,0:18:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連回家道別的時候\N也不摟一下我的肩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.67,0:18:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在幹什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.88,0:19:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牆壁裂縫吹來的風\N無處可躲的貧苦學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.35,0:19:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.97,0:20:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐\N待會要不要去喝杯咖啡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.65,0:20:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她今天也來了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.85,0:20:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩最近常常來耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.04,0:21:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.27,0:21:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切交給我處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.11,0:21:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹,我好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.54,0:21:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下洗手間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.25,0:21:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今\N只好直接跟五代談了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.29,0:21:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該不是抱著玩玩的心情吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.49,0:21:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.90,0:21:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.76,0:21:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼?\N會變成這樣都是你造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.23,0:21:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是男人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.37,0:21:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送她回家的時候\N至少也摟一下她的肩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.67,0:21:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了吧,懂了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.01,0:21:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.34,0:21:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記住,男生和女生\N道別時的表現是很重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.78,0:21:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.29,0:21:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分手時的表現…\N(''分手''音同''道別'')
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.50,0:22:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.91,0:22:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分手時的表現是很重要的…啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.58,0:22:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.38,0:22:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候跟三鷹交換的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.82,0:22:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是\N與其主動被她甩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.97,0:22:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江,跟妳在一起很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.58,0:22:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.69,0:23:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興\N你終於明白我的心意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.46,0:23:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了,改天見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.93,0:23:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦!改天見?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.30,0:23:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.71,0:23:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時序是聖誕夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.78,0:23:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是表達愛意的時刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.74,0:23:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茶茶丸吹起一陣羅曼史風暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.75,0:23:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.32,0:24:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「戀愛以膽量決勝負!\N五代打工大作戰」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.22,0:24:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是聖誕節故事善行篇的前篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.43,0:24:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我們互相凝視時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.07,0:24:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會有一道奇妙的旋律\N在心中迴響著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.92,0:24:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法用言語來表達愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.66,0:24:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好彈奏起了鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.10,0:24:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把夢丟進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.53,0:24:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我測量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.30,0:24:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.17,0:25:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用輕觸的嘴唇演奏著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.28,0:25:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平靜的合聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.29,0:25:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使擁抱著妳依然惆悵滿懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.46,0:25:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢見了Fantasy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.50,0:25:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開啟了只有我們兩人\N才看得見的門扉Fantasy
